[[File:Dunville's Whisky Pub Mirror 01.jpeg|thumb|A bar mirror bearing the logo of [[Dunville & Co#Dunville's Whisky|Dunville's Whiskey]].]] '''Bar mirrors''', also called '''pub mirrors''' in the [[United Kingdom]], are decorative mirrors usually hung in bars or pubs that bear an image. These images typically depict the logo of a brand of [[Distilled beverage|liquor]], [[beer]] or drinking establishment.
